            <div class="title">
                Discharged Service Personnel (Neurosis)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1943-04-20/debates/436ae336-7650-41b8-83f3-d3a41f9f0850/ChancellorOfTheDuchyOfLancaster" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
